7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"ISO 22301 Internal Audit Checklist"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:30:35+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"Wizms provides ISO 22301 audit checklist that helps the organizations in UAE, Dubai. Get ISO 22301 Certification in Dubai at best price."}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 22301 Internal Audit Checklist"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms has designed an ISO 22301 audit checklist, to maintain consistency in your company. An organization can also use it as an ISO 22301 audit checklist if they are preparing to undergo an official certification process."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 22301 Audit Checklist 1. Leadership"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms have a management oversight committee in place, along with a process that dictates how the committee will manage the ISO 22301 Certification from the time of creation all the way through implementation, maintenance, and the actual carrying out of plans."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Policies and objectives of ISO 22301 are aligned with the requirements of your organization. If a company in UAE have more intense legal/regulatory requirements, or customer and stakeholder requirements, then ISO 22301 policies must match your obligations."}],["$","p","5",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"2. Planning"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"ISO 22301 plan must define the following and note how each contributes to the development of your business continuity management system:"}],["$","p","7",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Requirements of company."}],["$","p","8",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Products or services you provide."}],["$","p","9",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Requirements of stakeholders."}],["$","p","10",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Companies legal/regulatory requirements. 3. Support"}],["$","p","11",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Wizms have a document management system that includes all the supporting documents related to every stage of ISO 22301 certification, from training to practice exercises. The ISO 22301 system manages and organizes relevant documents, easy to refer them, accessible to the right people."}],["$","p","12",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"4. Operation"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"To determine the risks associated with organizations business and controls to protect them, the company in Dubai need to document the risk, and threat assessment. (For assistance in evaluating residual risk and help in reducing it, try the Residual Risk online assessment tool.)"}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15"]}],"$L16"]}]}]
